00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.519
who died for me.

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:09.840
Wearing this,

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.280
I'll face them

00:02:11.719 --> 00:02:13.000
with dignity in the afterlife.

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:18.400
Today,

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:20.199
I'll kill you!

00:02:28.800 --> 00:02:29.400
It's fine.

00:02:35.199 --> 00:02:36.479
(The Frost Poison again.)

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.800
(The Emperor hides many secrets.)

00:02:39.479 --> 00:02:40.560
(I can't let him die yet.)

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:45.800
Guards!

00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:48.520
Guards!

00:02:54.199 --> 00:02:55.080
Your Grace.

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:56.800
Your Grace.

00:03:00.479 --> 00:03:01.400
Your Grace.

00:03:01.639 --> 00:03:03.680
I haven't even come to punish you yet,

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:05.759
yet you come to me now.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.280
Punish me later if you must.

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:08.599
Please save His Majesty.

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:11.120
What happened?

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:12.960
His Majesty has fallen ill.

00:03:13.199 --> 00:03:14.039
It's critical.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:15.240
Hurry!

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:16.080
Turn back!

00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:16.759
Yes.

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:20.599
What tea?

00:03:22.439 --> 00:03:23.120
Your Grace.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:25.360
It's the antidote
from the Prince Regent.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:27.479
These two maids always deliver it.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:29.680
The Prince Regent said

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:31.280
the tea should be served on time.

00:03:31.919 --> 00:03:33.360
Serve the tea

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:34.599
immediately!

00:03:34.919 --> 00:03:35.719
Your Grace,

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:36.960
it's not time yet.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:37.879
Serve it,

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:39.680
and the Prince Regent will punish me.

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:43.039
Have mercy, Your Grace.

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:45.039
I-I'll prepare it now.

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:46.039
What's really happening?

00:03:50.199 --> 00:03:50.759
Your Majesty.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.800
You handled this well.

00:03:59.719 --> 00:04:00.919
I'll spare you this time.

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:03.360
But if you dare

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:04.759
have treacherous thoughts,

00:04:05.879 --> 00:04:07.439
your death will be excruciating.

00:04:09.159 --> 00:04:09.879
I wouldn't dare.

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:15.680
You may leave.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.399
I'll attend to His Majesty alone.

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:31.879
Your Majesty,

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.160
