00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.680
(Is all this)

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:44.120
(heaven's punishment?)

00:04:44.959 --> 00:04:46.279
Who sent the antidote last night?

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:47.680
Your Majesty,

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:50.040
it was the new waiting maid

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:51.800
who sought help from Her Grace.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:54.759
Cheng Ge?

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:00.759
Summon her.

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:02.040
Yes.

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:10.000
Why summon me?

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.040
If you wanted me dead,

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:13.160
why saved me last night?

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.040
I balance debts clearly.

00:05:16.199 --> 00:05:17.800
You saved me from the Empress,

00:05:18.279 --> 00:05:19.279
and I repaid that debt.

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:20.959
We're even.

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:22.240
But

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:23.920
don't think saving you once

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.519
means I won't kill you later.

00:05:27.079 --> 00:05:28.040
If you want to kill me,

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:30.759
you had plenty of chances

00:05:31.399 --> 00:05:32.439
while I slept just now.

00:05:33.639 --> 00:05:34.279
I guess

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:37.480
you must have questions for me.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.160
Go ahead.

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:41.720
What's the question?

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:49.959
The Pingxiang rebellion.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:54.279
Back then,

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:57.399
the people of Pingxiang
rose against Shi Nan,

00:05:57.839 --> 00:05:58.639
the late Emperor.

00:06:00.079 --> 00:06:01.399
For the greater good,

00:06:01.399 --> 00:06:02.360
I granted them amnesty.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.000
Preposterous lies!

00:06:04.399 --> 00:06:06.399
On the very day you ascended the throne,

00:06:06.839 --> 00:06:07.920
